annotationA: 60S ribosomal protein L3; The L3 protein is a component of the large subunit of cytoplasmic ribosomes
annotationB: 40S ribosomal protein S30; Structural constituent of ribosome. It is involved in the biological process described with: mitotic spindle elongation; translation; mitotic spindle organization; Belongs to the eukaryotic ribosomal protein eS30 family
